#: ../../content/index.md:1
msgid "Welcome to the Resthome documentation"
msgstr "Bienvenue dans la documentation Resthome"

#: ../../content/index.md:4
msgid ""
"User documentation for the Resthome software (on Odoo) for nursing and care "
"homes (MR/MRS): residents, care, INAMI billing, eFact, MDA, eAgreement."
msgstr ""
"Documentation utilisateur de Resthome (sur Odoo) pour maisons de repos et de"
" soins (MR/MRS) : résidents, soins, facturation INAMI, eFact, MDA, "
"eAgreement."

#: ../../content/index.md:7
msgid ""
"**Resthome** is the management software for **nursing homes (MR)** and "
"**nursing and care homes (MRS)**, published by LPLG **on Odoo** — residents,"
" care, meals, INAMI/mutuality billing and the Belgian eHealth exchanges "
"(eFact, MDA, eAgreement), all in one place. This documentation guides you "
"day by day, step by step, with screenshots."
msgstr ""
"**Resthome** est le logiciel de gestion pour **maisons de repos (MR)** et "
"**maisons de repos et de soins (MRS)**, édité par LPLG **sur Odoo** — "
"résidents, soins, repas, facturation INAMI/mutuelle et échanges eHealth "
"belges (eFact, MDA, eAgreement), le tout au même endroit. Cette "
"documentation vous accompagne au quotidien, étape par étape, avec des "
"captures d'écran."

#: ../../content/index.md:17
msgid "Getting started"
msgstr "Premiers pas"

#: ../../content/index.md:18
msgid ""
"Log in, discover the apps and the dashboard, and find your way around a "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Se connecter, découvrir les applications et le tableau de bord, et se "
"repérer dans un écran."

#: ../../content/index.md:21
msgid "The billing journey"
msgstr "Le parcours de facturation"

#: ../../content/index.md:22
msgid ""
"The big picture: admission → MDA → eAgreement → Katz → eFact → payment."
msgstr ""
"La vue d'ensemble : admission → MDA → eAgreement → Katz → eFact → paiement."

#: ../../content/index.md:25
msgid "Residents"
msgstr "Résidents"

#: ../../content/index.md:26
msgid ""
"Admission, stay, Katz and geriatric assessments, rooms and the condition "
"report."
msgstr ""
"Admission, séjour, évaluations Katz et gériatriques, chambres et état des "
"lieux."

#: ../../content/index.md:29
msgid "Billing"
msgstr "Facturation"

#: ../../content/index.md:30
msgid "Billing periods, INAMI packages, supplements, absences and invoices."
msgstr ""
"Périodes de facturation, forfaits INAMI, suppléments, absences et factures."

#: ../../content/index.md:33
msgid "eHealth"
msgstr "eHealth"

#: ../../content/index.md:34
msgid ""
"Insurability (MDA), electronic invoicing (eFact) and agreements "
"(eAgreement)."
msgstr ""
"Assurabilité (MDA), facturation électronique (eFact) et accords "
"(eAgreement)."

#: ../../content/index.md:37
msgid "Care"
msgstr "Soins"

#: ../../content/index.md:38
msgid "Clinical record, prescriptions, care plans and clinical registers."
msgstr ""
"Dossier clinique, prescriptions, plans de soins et registres cliniques."

#: ../../content/index.md:41
msgid "Meals"
msgstr "Repas"

#: ../../content/index.md:42
msgid ""
"Menus and diets, meal distribution, nutrition monitoring and the family "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Menus et régimes, distribution des repas, suivi nutritionnel et portail "
"familles."

#: ../../content/index.md:45
msgid "Resident documents"
msgstr "Documents du résident"

#: ../../content/index.md:46
msgid "Automatic document folders per resident and attachment centralization."
msgstr ""
"Dossiers documentaires automatiques par résident et centralisation des "
"pièces jointes."

#: ../../content/index.md:49
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Configuration"

#: ../../content/index.md:50
msgid "All the settings: residents, billing, eHealth, meals and documents."
msgstr ""
"Tous les réglages : résidents, facturation, eHealth, repas et documents."

#: ../../content/index.md:54
msgid "A precise question?"
msgstr "Une question précise ?"

#: ../../content/index.md:57
msgid ""
"Use the **search bar** at the top, the **[FAQ](faq.md)** or the "
"**[Glossary](glossaire.md)**. This documentation is public and written to be"
" readable by AI assistants — you can ask your question in plain language."
msgstr ""
"Utilisez la **barre de recherche** en haut, la **[FAQ](faq.md)** ou le "
"**[Glossaire](glossaire.md)**. Cette documentation est publique et conçue "
"pour être lisible par les assistants IA — vous pouvez poser votre question "
"en langage naturel."

